title: DAY6 Reveals New Teaser Image Of Sungjin For Upcoming March Release | Soompi
text:
Pin Display.Sharethrough.Soompi.1x1 
After releasing new tracks in January and February, DAY6 is now gearing up to release their third release of the year! 
On February 27, the group released a teaser through their official Twitter, featuring member Sungjin along with the title of their new track “How Can I Say.”
